column4: Can anyone help me with wine install I get this when i apt-get updateFailed to fetch http://wine.budgetdedicated.com/apt/dists/dapper/main/binary-amd64/Packages.gz  404 Not Found
I thought there's no wine for amd64.
nope, look here, there's no amd64 repository: http://wine.budgetdedicated.com/apt/dists/dapper/main/
but there's a howto for wine 32 bit on amd64 in here: http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=191205
